  "description": "A cascading stream flows over moss-covered rocks in a lush, green forest setting. Water tumbles down a rocky incline, forming small waterfalls and rapids. The rocks are heavily coated in vibrant green moss, creating a velvety texture. Ferns and other greenery surround the stream, adding to the dense foliage. A wooden boardwalk or bridge is faintly visible in the upper right corner, suggesting a path through the forest. The lighting is soft and diffused, enhancing the tranquil and natural atmosphere.",
